{"tid":2140789,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"要求政府邀請李克強加入管理龔如心千億遺產 華懋慈善基金稱對方樂意受邀","createTime":"2020-08-05T08:30:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-20T14:25:14.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c482e9ee24df729422efea3b9cb85aebec385334","tid":2140789,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T08:30:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200805/JHCKI4GDRCTUR52GPE3MG5MWNY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200805%2FJHCKI4GDRCTUR52GPE3MG5MWNY%2F&d=Iz1eZ%2FSDqTYQUikxH7ZeamDcYOQIx6XO0JIcXsozN2c%3D&h=a00ce7c2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200805%2FJHCKI4GDRCTUR52GPE3MG5MWNY%2F&h=386a7c8e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200805/JHCKI4GDRCTUR52GPE3MG5MWNY/</a><br />\n<br />\n華懋集團前主席龔如心的千億遺產案，受託遺產的華懋慈善基金要求按照龔遺願，邀請國務院總理李克強及聯合國秘書長加入管理，以設立類似諾貝爾獎的獎項。基金今透露有人員曾接觸外交部，獲回應指總理李克強應該會樂意擔任有關工作，惟外交部認為在目前的政治環境，有關要求最好由香港政府提出。基金今要求高等法院頒令，指示律政司司長鄭若驊立即提出邀請，惟法官聆訊後並無頒下命令，案件明年中再訊。"},{"pid":"ab7d6623ad5047c62f7a64da354d52de4d5ccd33","tid":2140789,"uid":123848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T08:44:42.000Z","msg":"死咗咁耐都可以改遺囑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"300693a62b2c4025f7b4801a339db5cca12eade3","tid":2140789,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T08:45:47.000Z","msg":"邀請國務院總理李克強及<span class=\"red\">聯合國秘書長</span>加入管理<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95c05c021e0653a71a6c879ab47b184fe58e6f90","tid":2140789,"uid":332804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T09:01:21.000Z","msg":"要強仔唔要雜種？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"269d8bd467f2bdcd34259b0fee2e48e0ea5927c1","tid":2140789,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"95c05c02